<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-slate-50 section-bg-pattern">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="section-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl" data-aos="fade-up" data-en="The Arzu Difference" data-ar="ما يميزنا في Arzu" data-de="Der Arzu-Unterschied" data-ro="Diferența Arzu">The Arzu Difference</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100" data-en="We don't just offer trips; we craft experiences. With years of expertise and a deep love for the sea, we promise you a journey filled with wonder, safety, and personalized care." data-ar="نحن لا نقدم رحلات فحسب، بل نصنع تجارب لا تُنسى. بسنوات من الخبرة والحب العميق للبحر، نعدك برحلة مليئة بالدهشة والأمان والاهتمام الشخصي." data-de="Wir bieten nicht nur Ausflüge an; wir schaffen Erlebnisse. Mit jahrelanger Erfahrung und einer tiefen Liebe zum Meer versprechen wir Ihnen eine Reise voller Wunder, Sicherheit und persönlicher Betreuung." data-ro="Nu oferim doar excursii; creăm experiențe. Cu ani de experiență și o dragoste profundă pentru mare, vă promitem o călătorie plină de minuni, siguranță și îngrijire personalizată.">We don't just offer trips; we craft experiences...</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div data-aos="fade-right" class="relative">
                <img src="~/images/about.jpg" alt="Happy tourists on a boat" class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-full h-auto object-cover" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/600x400/006064/ffffff?text=Arzu+Adventures';">
