            </div>
            <div data-aos="fade-left" class="space-y-6">
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-ship"></i></div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="feature-title" data-en="Expert-Led Journeys" data-ar="رحلات بقيادة خبراء" data-de="Von Experten geführte Reisen" data-ro="Călătorii conduse de experți">Expert-Led Journeys</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600" data-en="Our guides are seasoned sea lovers who know the hidden gems of the Red Sea." data-ar="مرشدونا هم من عشاق البحر المتمرسين الذين يعرفون كنوز البحر الأحمر الخفية." data-de="Unsere Guides sind erfahrene Meeresliebhaber, die die verborgenen Schätze des Roten Meeres kennen." data-ro="Ghizii noștri sunt iubitori de mare experimentați, care cunosc bijuteriile ascunse ale Mării Roșii.">Our guides are seasoned sea lovers who know the hidden gems of the Red Sea.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i></div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="feature-title" data-en="Safety is Our Priority" data-ar="السلامة هي أولويتنا" data-de="Sicherheit ist unsere Priorität" data-ro="Siguranța este prioritatea noastră">Safety is Our Priority</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600" data-en="We adhere to the highest safety standards to ensure you can relax and enjoy your adventure." data-ar="نلتزم بأعلى معايير السلامة لنضمن لك الاسترخاء والاستمتاع بمغامرتك." data-de="Wir halten uns an die höchsten Sicherheitsstandards, damit Sie sich entspannen und Ihr Abenteuer genießen können." data-ro="Respectăm cele mai înalte standarde de siguranță pentru a ne asigura că vă puteți relaxa și bucura de aventură.">We adhere to the highest safety standards to ensure you can relax and enjoy your adventure.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-gem"></i></div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="feature-title" data-en="Tailored Experiences" data-ar="تجارب مخصصة" data-de="Maßgeschneiderte Erlebnisse" data-ro="Experiențe personalizate">Tailored Experiences</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600" data-en="From private yacht charters to group snorkeling trips, we customize every detail for you." data-ar="من استئجار اليخوت الخاصة إلى رحلات الغطس الجماعية، نقوم بتخصيص كل التفاصيل من أجلك." data-de="Von privaten Yachtchartern bis hin zu Gruppenschnorchelausflügen passen wir jedes Detail für Sie an." data-ro="De la închirieri de iahturi private la excursii de snorkeling în grup, personalizăm fiecare detaliu pentru dvs.">From private yacht charters to group snorkeling trips, we customize every detail for you.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<section id="services" class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="section-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl" data-aos="fade-up" data-en="Our Premier Services" data-ar="خدماتنا المتميزة" data-de="Unsere Premium-Services" data-ro="Serviciile noastre premium">Our Premier Services</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100" data-en="Adventures tailored for every sea enthusiast." data-ar="مغامرات مصممة لكل محب للبحر." data-de="Abenteuer für jeden Meeresliebhaber." data-ro="Aventuri personalizate pentru fiecare pasionat de mare.">Adventures tailored for every sea enthusiast.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
            <div class="service-card" data-aos="fade-up">
